# Standard User Journey


## Standard user logs in

* Open the landing page of the store Saucedemo
* Check that the landing page of the store is succesfully opened
* Fill in the standard user details and attempt to login
* Verify if whether  standard user has succesfully logged in

## Standard user can add products to the cart
* Verify if whether  standard user has succesfully logged in
* Select a product or two to add to the cart
* View cart
* Verify if whether the previously selected products are indeed the cart

## Standard user can checkout products added to the cart
* Verify if whether  standard user has succesfully logged in
* Select a product or two to add to the cart
* View cart
* Verify if whether the previously selected products are indeed in the cart
* Verify if whether the user is lead to a checkout page and is prompted to fill in a  form
* Ensure the standard user fills in the form accordingly and accurately
* Verify that the standard user is lead to an order Overview page after filling in the form and clicking continue
* Verify that the details of the order are correct and click on the continue button
* Verify that your order has been placed by getting a confirmation message on screen
* Verify that your order was placed by ensuring your cart is now clean

## Standard user can remove products from the cart
* Verify if whether  standard user has succesfully logged in
* Select a product or two to add to the cart
* View cart
* Verify if whether the previously selected products are indeed the cart
* Remove each product in your cart by clicking the remove button on each product
* Verify if whether the products have been removed by ensuring your cart is now empty

## Standard user can reset the App state
* Verify if whether  standard user has succesfully logged in
* Select a product or two to add to the cart
* View cart
* Standard user resets app state
* Verify if whether the app state is reset by ensuring that our cart is clean

## Standard user can logout Succesfully
* Verify if whether  standard user has succesfully logged in
* Select a product or two to add to the cart
* View cart
* Standard user logs out
* Verify if whether we have succesfully logged out and are now on the store's homepage being prompted to log in again 